<L>__{interior 11th street district house night}
<A>__{camera finds kimble in an interview room. he is in "why" shock. "why her." "why me?" says nothing. two detectives: kelly and rosetti. kelly, the questioner, is overweight, aggressive. he shifts his gun on his hip so he can sit down.}
